{"tid":2171702,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"商台就嚟六十一歲生日，至今仍然做左非常錯誤嘅決定","createTime":"2020-08-24T06:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T09:52:14.000Z","uid":220066,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b7401a387086ad22aa983dc45c3657e57e5ade","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"就係換左麻利同迪偉加入做口水多過浪花<br />\n轉換左班底都已經接近四年<br />\n唔少觀眾被逼習慣接受新主持風格<br />\n但係口水焦點集中係迪偉同Do姐身上<br />\n而麻利同傑豬完全係無乜作用<br />\n自在做下小丑比迪偉同Do姐撚<br />\n回想番艾粒同do姐做節目<br />\n大家都會敢放去互相串對方<br />\n呢個就係聽眾最鐘意既地方<br />\n但係至今換左班底之後<br />\n口水一直係走緊下波<br />\n傑豬同麻利正係識得擦do姐鞋<br />\n慘到而家嘉賓環節正係得do姐做曬<br />\n將成個節目質素拉抵曬<br />\n而聖艾粒同時都走緊下波<br />\n環節成日轉來轉去，證明已經乾曬糖<br />\n大家兩邊節目質素比以前係hea左好多<br />\n<br />\n唯一解決方法就係艾粒番去口水再拍番do姐<br />\n至於迪偉都係做番夜晚節目會比較適合<br />\n麻利同傑豬自己開番個節目做仲好<br />\n唔好再污染口水啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9i0n70y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9i0n70y.png&h=a54f8f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWL7zFA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWL7zFA.png&h=7b32ae45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評：艾粒番去拍番do姐<br />\n<br />\n負評：比新組合一個機會仲好啦"},{"pid":"bdbd4bb37529234686e9c1ce617ecba17912d356","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe1fcc8478244b6ba7c993ba6a011fca62a1bc85","tid":2171702,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"叫麻利講SRT 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講得多都悶"},{"pid":"bda44571842025338c0f137f466b885257884c37","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1fcc8478244b6ba7c993ba6a011fca62a1bc85","tid":2171702,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"叫麻利講SRT 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講得多都悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:40:59.000Z","msg":"而家直頭唔聽口水，好撚悶"},{"pid":"e727d555886da722a2c349dc6b3609a71ac3ac27","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5c5ea395e2b7af3bc34b4d27fc017d5450fa3a1","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c86cd932f1ab1fd509c612776d32399dbbc6b0e6","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:54:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f85b7e170a55b4fcff65e5cbcb0712baad9359f","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"798cb2b5c21fdd34fc0f27be30d623b4091ac84d","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99de0a9ed2fcf7c2d9fa5ff83a6ac7d88f6d038b","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcca268d855a2295c29f6fa1055ebab4bb438957","tid":2171702,"uid":115782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"艾粒自己無問題<br />\n成日轉環節關唔關唔請嘉賓上去事<br />\n同埋唔想有環節側重俾長毛贏<br />\n但估明星果part真心悶<br />\n<br />\n(口水無聽好耐）"},{"pid":"691b57d9c114f7de805921d9d6c8b25651cf50be","tid":2171702,"uid":52654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"口水愈來愈似婦女節目，隔一排聽幾分鐘就熄左"},{"pid":"e838e7983811fe3e723a1ecff42d9685717aa39f","tid":2171702,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcca268d855a2295c29f6fa1055ebab4bb438957","tid":2171702,"uid":115782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"艾粒自己無問題<br />\n成日轉環節關唔關唔請嘉賓上去事<br />\n同埋唔想有環節側重俾長毛贏<br />\n但估明星果part真心悶<br />\n<br />\n(口水無聽好耐）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:52:14.000Z","msg